---
title: Harvest Bolognese Pasta with Baby Tomatoes
description: We've put a twist on this Italian classic by adding zucchini and fresh baby tomatoes. All the ingredients blend together to create an incredible depth of flavour!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pates-a-la-bolognaise-aux-legumes-9684d137.jpg
